en_460780_0	The Summit under the theme Indian Ocean Defines our Future, will be held on the 11th and 12th of this month at the Temple Trees in Colombo.
en_460780_1	President Maithripala Sirisena is scheduled to make the inaugural address at the Summit on the 11th of this month.
en_460780_2	Prime Minister Ranil Wickremasinghe will deliver the Keynote Address of the Summit.
en_460780_3	The UN Special Representative on Oceans Peter Thompson is scheduled to address the summit.
en_460780_4	It has been jointly organized by the Prime Minister’s office, Foreign Affairs Ministry, Lakshman Kadirgamar Institute and the UN’s office on Narcotics and Crimes.
